Hamdan bin Mohammed: &ldquo;The UAE&rsquo;s forward-looking leadership has made it a top global destination for living and business.&rdquo;
Over 1,000 millionaires relocated to Dubai in 2018.
Crown Prince of Dubai, Sheikh Hamdan bin Mohammed bin Rashid Al Maktoum, credits the UAE&rsquo;s robust investment and economic landscape to its leadership&rsquo;s visionary approach. He highlights their commitment to the well-being of residents, visitors, and investors, along with fostering innovation, as key factors in establishing the UAE as a premier lifestyle and business hub.
